original_font_information.description: Sansita One is a tasty new Omnibus-Type font designed by Pablo Cosgaya. The flavor of Sansita One's lowercase explores the relationship between typography and calligraphy. The elegance of Sansita One's uppercase makes this an excellent choice for packaging, brief texts, branding and slogans.
